# 🍽️ Restaurant Management System API

A backend REST API for managing restaurant operations including orders, menu, inventory, tables, and reservations. Built with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👤 Authentication & Authorization
- User registration and login
- JWT-based authentication
- Role-based access control (Admin, Staff, Cashier)

### 🍔 Menu Management
- Create, update, delete menu items
- Categorize food items (food, drink, dessert)
- Link menu items to inventory ingredients

### 📦 Inventory Management
- Add and manage stock items
- Track ingredient quantities
- Automatic stock deduction when orders are placed
- Low stock monitoring (extendable)

### 🧾 Order System
- Place customer orders
- Calculate total price automatically
- Link orders to menu items
- Prevent orders when stock is insufficient
- Order status tracking (pending, preparing, served, completed)

### 🪑 Table Management
- Create restaurant tables
- Track table capacity
- Manage table status (available, occupied, reserved)
- Assign orders to tables

### 📅 Reservation System
- Reserve tables for customers
- Automatic table assignment based on capacity
- Prevent double booking
- Store reservation time and guest details

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- JSON Web Token (JWT)
- bcryptjs
- dotenv

