## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1. Clone Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Afolabismart8/CodeAlpha_Restaurant-Management-System.git
cd restaurant-management-system
2. Install Dependencies
npm install
3. Create Environment Variables
Create a .env file in root:
PORT=3000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key

4. Run Server
npm run dev

Server runs on:
http://localhost:3000

📌 API Endpoints
Auth
POST /api/register
POST /api/login
Menu
GET    /api/menu
POST   /api/menu
Orders
POST   /api/order
GET    /api/order
Inventory
GET    /api/inventory
POST   /api/inventory
PATCH  /api/inventory/:id
DELETE /api/inventory/:id
Tables
GET    /api/table
POST   /api/table
PATCH  /api/table/:id

🔄 System Flow
Admin creates menu items
Inventory items are added (ingredients)
Menu items are linked to inventory
Customers place orders
System checks inventory automatically
Stock is deducted after order placement
Tables are assigned and tracked

